title: Greater Is Coming
itunes:title: Greater Is Coming
description:
When you go through a difficult season, remember that the trouble is only temporary. What the enemy is using to try to set you back, God is going to use to your advantage. Get ready—greater things are coming!Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love. To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
